snow white is a 1916 american silent romantic fantasy film directed by j. searle dawley . it was adapted by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ames from his own 1912 broadway play snow white and the seven dwarfs , which was in turn adapted from the 1812 fairy tale ( as collected by the grimm brothers ) . the film stars marguerite clark and creighton hale , clark reprising her stage role . fifteen years old when he saw it , walt disney was inspired to make it the subject of his first feature-length animated film .